videos.description: Miami's great ball movement creates an open 3-pointer for Chris Lykes.
videos.headline: Lykes drains it from deep

videos.description: Terrell Brown muscles to the hoop for a Pittsburgh dunk.
videos.headline: Brown throws down

videos.description: Pittsburgh's Jared Wilson-Frame forces Miami's fourth turnover and responds with an and-1.
videos.headline: Wilson-Frame creates 3-point play

videos.description: Bruce Brown stuffs Khameron Davis and chucks it down the court for Eduka Izundu to slam it home.
videos.headline: Izundu's sends in one-handed slam

videos.description: Shamiel Stevenson drives along the baseline and finishes with the reverse lay in for Pittsburgh.
videos.headline: Stevenson throws up reverse layup

videos.description: Miami's Dewan Huell comes flying in for one-handed putback dunk.
videos.headline: Huell pushes the rim
